<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221826>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 16. Savigniorrhipis topographicus new species. Male from São Jorge: 9 — retrolateral aspect of pedipalp; 10 — frontal aspect of pedipalp; 11 — prolateral aspect of pedipalp; 12 — dorsal aspect of tibia; 13 — dorsal aspect of suprategular apophysis; 14 — lateral aspect of the prosoma. Female from São Jorge: 15 — ventral aspect of the epigynum; 16 — dorsal aspect of vulva. Scale bars = 0, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221826/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

